fn filter

(self, predicate: P) -> Filter where Self: Sized, P: FnMut(&Self::Item) -> bool, { Filter::new(self, predicate) }

fn map<B, F>(self, f: F) -> Map<Self, F>
    where
        Self: Sized,
        F: FnMut(Self::Item) -> B,
    {
        Map::new(self, f)
    }

fn sum<S>(self) -> S
    where
        Self: Sized,
        S: Sum<Self::Item>,
    {
        Sum::sum(self)
    }
